signatures.text: infix fun <T> Array<out T>.intersect( other: Iterable<T>): Set<T>
signatures.desc: Returns a set containing all elements that are contained by both this array and the specified collection.

signatures.text: infix fun <T> Iterable<T>.intersect( other: Iterable<T>): Set<T>
signatures.desc: Returns a set containing all elements that are contained by both this collection and the specified collection.
